articles.author: Guardian staff reporter
articles.title: Erik Lamela fires Sevilla past Juventus and into Europa League final - The Guardian
articles.description: Sevilla will face Roma in the Europa League final after seeing off Juventus 2-1 in the semi-final for a 3-2 aggregate victory
articles.content: Europa League thoroughbreds Sevilla fought back to reach yet another final as substitute Érik Lamela scored with a fabulous header five minutes into extra time to earn a gritty 2-1 win over Juventus … [+5920 chars]

articles.author: Joe Krishnan
articles.title: Novak Djokovic's coach shouts 'what the f**k is wrong with you' in heated Italian Open row - Express
articles.description: Novak Djokovic received a verbal lashing from his coach Goran Ivanisevic as tensions threatened to boil over at the Italian Open in Rome.
